    <title>Manjaro安装</title>
    <url>/2021/07/11/manjaro%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Manjaro-Reinstall"><a href="#Manjaro-Reinstall" class="headerlink" title="Manjaro Reinstall"></a>Manjaro Reinstall</h1><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><blockquote>
<p>分区</p>
</blockquote>
<p>格式    挂载点    标签</p>
<p>fat16(windows)   /boot/efi   boot<br>ext4    /</p>
<h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><blockquote>
<p>换源</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syyu</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S vim  proxychains zsh wget git typora yay</span><br><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/pacman.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">Server = https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/<span class="variable">$arch</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syyu</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S archlinuxcn-keyring</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>输入法</p>
</blockquote>
<p>安装fcitx5（输入法框架）</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S fcitx5-im</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>配置fcitx5的环境变量：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~/.pam_environment</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INPUT_METHOD  DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">GTK_IM_MODULE DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">QT_IM_MODULE  DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">XMODIFIERS    DEFAULT=\@im=fcitx5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装fcitx5-rime（输入法引擎）</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S fcitx5-rime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装rime-cloverpinyin（输入方案）</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S rime-cloverpinyin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>重启</p>
<p>创建并写入rime-cloverpinyin的输入方案：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nano ~/.local/share/fcitx5/rime/default.custom.yaml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>内容为：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">patch:</span><br><span class="line">  &quot;menu/page_size&quot;: 8</span><br><span class="line">  schema_list:</span><br><span class="line">    - schema: clover</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装中文维基百科词库：</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S fcitx5-pinyin-zhwiki-rime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><a href="https://github.com/fkxxyz/rime-cloverpinyin/wiki/linux">wiki</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>代理</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chromium --proxy-server=&quot;socks5://127.0.0.1:51837&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/proxychains.conf</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#末尾加上</span></span><br><span class="line">	socks5 127.0.0.1 51837</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<blockquote>
<p>zsh</p>
</blockquote>
<p>更换bash为zsh</p>
<p>安装ohmyzsh</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/raw/master/tools/install.sh -O - | sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装zsh-syntax-highlighting：提供命令高亮</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git <span class="variable">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装autosuggestions：记住之前使用过的命令</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions <span class="variable">$&#123;ZSH_CUSTOM:-~/.oh-my-zsh/custom&#125;</span>/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim .zshrc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	plugins=(git zsh-syntax-highlighting zsh-autosuggestions extract)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> .zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S thefuck</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># .zshrc中source $ZSH/oh-my-zsh.sh下一行</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">eval</span> $(thefuck --<span class="built_in">alias</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>软件</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S ranger</span><br><span class="line">yay -S deepin.com.qq.im.light <span class="comment"># yay下载失败了，去应用商店下可以</span></span><br><span class="line">yay -S wqy-microhei wqy-zenhei <span class="comment"># 缺失字体，不然上面的QQ会乱码</span></span><br><span class="line">yay -S wps-office ttf-wps-fonts wps-office-mui-zh-cn <span class="comment"># AUR源选择wps-office-cn(这样下载更快)，目前fcitx5不需要改配置文件就可以输入中文了</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>美化</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yay -S latte-dock</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 登录开启数字锁</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装systemd-numlockontty</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> numLockOnTty.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>设置-&gt;工作空间行为-&gt;桌面特效</p>
<p>破碎、魔灯</p>
<p>修改用户文件夹名称为英文：</p>
<p>先去手动修改文件夹名称，然后在 设置 -&gt; 应用程序 -&gt; 地点 修改</p>
<h2 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h2><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/64960991">Re：从零开始的Manjaro配置</a></p>
<p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/114296129">Manjaro-KDE配置全攻略</a></p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Linux</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Manjaro</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
