    <title>Scoop安装及配置</title>
    <url>/2021/07/11/scoop%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Scoop安装及配置"><a href="#Scoop安装及配置" class="headerlink" title="Scoop安装及配置"></a>Scoop安装及配置</h1><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>先开全局模式，以免连接中断</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -scope CurrentUser <span class="comment"># 开权限</span></span><br><span class="line">Invoke-Expression (New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString(<span class="string">&#x27;https://get.scoop.sh&#x27;</span>) <span class="comment"># 下载安装</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>更多参考<a href="https://scoop.sh/">官网</a>,软件默认安装在用户目录的scoop文件夹下</p>
<h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop checkup <span class="comment"># 检查潜在的问题</span></span><br><span class="line">	scoop install 7zip</span><br><span class="line">	scoop install innounp</span><br><span class="line">	scoop install dark</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 设置代理</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop config proxy 127.0.0.1:51837</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 移除代理</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># scoop config rm proxy</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看可识别的bucket</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop bucket known</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 添加bucket</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop bucket add extras</span><br><span class="line">scoop bucket add nerd-fonts</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看已有bucket</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop bucket list</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装软件</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install aria2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/hongdada/p/11844277.html">Window包管理工具Scoop</a></p>
]]></content>
