    <title>windows terminal设置alias别名</title>
    <url>/2021/07/11/windows%20terminal%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEalias/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="windows-terminal设置alias别名"><a href="#windows-terminal设置alias别名" class="headerlink" title="windows terminal设置alias别名"></a>windows terminal设置alias别名</h1><ol>
<li><p>打开 PowerShell ，运行 <code>echo $profile</code>，会输出一个文件路径，创建这个文件。</p>
</li>
<li><p>用notepad++打开这个文件，按如下格式设置别名：</p>
</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="built_in">alias</span>别名 &#123;命令&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>例如</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">nb</span></span> &#123;jupyter notebook&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>（第一次更改后打开terminal会报错）以管理员身份打开 PowerShell，执行 <code>Set-ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned</code>。</li>
<li>重启Powershell</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>文件代码</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> nb &#123;jupyter notebook&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> da &#123;</span><br><span class="line">H:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> \</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> workplace\dataAnalysis\Scripts\</span><br><span class="line">.\activate</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> tor &#123;</span><br><span class="line">H:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> \</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> .\workplace\pytorch\Scripts\</span><br><span class="line">.\activate</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> tf &#123;</span><br><span class="line">H:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> \</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> .\workplace\tensorflow\Scripts\</span><br><span class="line">.\activate</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> de &#123;deactivate&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> code &#123;&amp; <span class="string">&#x27;C:\Users\57211\AppData\Local\Programs\Microsoft VS Code\Code.exe&#x27;</span> --proxy-server=<span class="string">&quot;socks5://127.0.0.1:51837&quot;</span> --host-resolver-rules=<span class="string">&quot;MAP * ~NOTFOUND , EXCLUDE 127.0.0.1&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> blog &#123;</span><br><span class="line">D:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> \workplace\BLOG</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
