    <title>conda配置及常用操作</title>
    <url>/2021/07/20/conda%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%8A%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="conda配置及常用操作"><a href="#conda配置及常用操作" class="headerlink" title="conda配置及常用操作"></a>conda配置及常用操作</h1><p>新建环境</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create -n name python=x.x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>添加镜像源</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/free/</span><br><span class="line">conda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main/</span><br><span class="line">conda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud/conda-forge/</span><br><span class="line">conda config --add channels https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud/pytorch/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>查看channel</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda config --show channels</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>本地安装</p>
<p>当因为网速问题下载失败后，用提示的链接通过浏览器下载，然后本地安装</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda install --use-local pkg_</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
